Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:24.57,0:01:29.32,OP_jp,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,光を信じた 希望の先へ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:29.64,0:01:34.43,OP_jp,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,明日への道は 終わらないNever ends
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:34.80,0:01:39.44,OP_jp,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,瞳に映した 誓いの欠片
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:39.78,0:01:44.73,OP_jp,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,暗黒の渦を 切り裂くTestament
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:44.96,0:01:51.42,OP_jp,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,神さえも超えて 叫んだら
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:52.00,0:01:55.28,OP_jp,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,探し出して
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:55.78,0:02:01.53,OP_jp,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,守るべきもの 握りしめた右手で
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:01.92,0:02:06.22,OP_jp,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Far away どんな遠くでも届くよ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:06.22,0:02:11.68,OP_jp,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,大事なもの 無くさない想いなら
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:12.11,0:02:18.78,OP_jp,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Every way 枯れた世界から 進めるはずさ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:19.09,0:02:21.72,OP_jp,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,未来へ 走れ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:00.10,0:00:00.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:24.57,0:01:29.32,OP_cn,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,相信那道光明 朝希望進發
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:29.64,0:01:34.43,OP_cn,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,通向明天的道路 永不終結Never ends
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:34.80,0:01:39.44,OP_cn,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,映襯在瞳孔中的 誓言之欠片
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:39.78,0:01:44.73,OP_cn,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,劈開黑暗的漩渦 Testament
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:44.96,0:01:51.42,OP_cn,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,超越神靈 放聲嘶吼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:52.00,0:01:55.28,OP_cn,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,四處追尋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:55.78,0:02:01.53,OP_cn,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,用緊握的右手守護珍愛之物
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:01.92,0:02:06.22,OP_cn,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Far away 無論多遙遠都能傳遞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:06.22,0:02:11.68,OP_cn,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,如果不想失去這份寶貴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:12.11,0:02:18.78,OP_cn,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Every way 一定能走出枯萎的世界
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:19.09,0:02:21.72,OP_cn,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,向未來躍進
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:00.10,0:00:00.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:00.10,0:00:00.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:00.10,0:00:00.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:00.10,0:00:00.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:03.16,0:00:03.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,刃更
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:04.83,0:00:07.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不要..振作一點啊 喂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:08.17,0:00:11.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,即便是勇者一族 也不過是個氣數已盡的廢人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:12.10,0:00:13.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,出乎意料地脆弱呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:17.66,0:00:20.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,絕對不可原諒..你們怎敢！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:21.21,0:00:22.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,誒 不錯不錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:25.72,0:00:28.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不快點治療可就遲了哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:31.97,0:00:32.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你懂了嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:33.60,0:00:36.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,這就是你的決斷所造成的結果
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:36.87,0:00:37.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我的..
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:38.42,0:00:40.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,讓周圍的人受牽連 受傷害
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:40.79,0:00:42.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,即便如此 你也要為了自己的復仇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:43.28,0:00:45.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,而繼續這場毫無勝算的戰鬥麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:47.66,0:00:49.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不過呢 同樣通過你的決斷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:50.05,0:00:52.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,也能夠馬上結束這一切呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:54.76,0:00:59.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,刃更 對不起 對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:00.60,0:01:01.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,對不起..
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:00.10,0:00:00.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:34.47,0:02:39.44,title,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fad(720,720)}直到悲傷歸零為止
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:00.10,0:00:00.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:36.94,0:02:37.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,情況如何？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:37.94,0:02:40.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,傷口合上了 脈搏也正常
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:41.13,0:02:42.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,太好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:42.91,0:02:44.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你好好考慮一下吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:47.62,0:02:50.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,接下來只要好好休息 恢復體力..
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:51.15,0:02:51.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,澪大人？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:52.47,0:02:54.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,啊 好像有點發燒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:54.61,0:02:56.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,這可不好 去吃點藥吧..
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:56.39,0:02:59.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,沒事的 我回房間休息一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:59.65,0:03:00.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,之後就拜託你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:01.17,0:03:02.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:05.12,0:03:06.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,刃更先生！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:08.91,0:03:12.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,對不起 如果我能到的早一些的話..
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:12.75,0:03:14.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不 你已經幫很多了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:15.16,0:03:18.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,但是您真厲害 居然這麼快就恢復意識了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:19.74,0:03:23.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我們一族是用特殊的訓練來鍛煉身體的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:25.07,0:03:26.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,從小時候開始就是..
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:30.08,0:03:31.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好 刃更到此為止
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:34.95,0:03:36.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,刃更好厲害
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:37.71,0:03:39.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不愧是迅的兒子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:40.32,0:03:43.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不僅僅是劍 還有他那與生俱來的力量
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:44.07,0:03:45.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那孩子是下一代的希望
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:46.31,0:03:47.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不得了了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:49.23,0:03:50.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,發生了什麼事？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:50.70,0:03:51.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,聖域之魔劍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:51.95,0:03:53.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,布倫希爾德的封印被解開了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:54.22,0:03:56.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,聖域之魔劍是那把..
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:56.64,0:03:59.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是封印遠古的邪精靈的劍啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:59.92,0:04:00.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,到底是誰幹的？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:00.90,0:04:01.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是清斗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:02.46,0:04:03.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是那傢伙麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:03.79,0:04:07.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,他從過去就對和魔族停戰一事抱有不滿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:07.77,0:04:09.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,難道他想單槍匹馬前往魔界？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:09.98,0:04:13.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,沒那麼簡單！被封印的邪精靈奪取了他的身體
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:13.56,0:04:15.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,朝著這個村子裏來了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:15.07,0:04:15.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你說什麼！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:23.00,0:04:25.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,把孩子們..快把孩子送去安全的地方！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:25.86,0:04:28.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,可惡 偏偏這個時候迅不在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:52.14,0:04:54.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,柚希！！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:12.31,0:05:13.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,刃更先生？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:13.90,0:05:15.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,對了 澪呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:15.33,0:05:16.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,說是有些發燒 回房間休息了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:17.24,0:05:19.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,發燒？又是詛咒嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:19.62,0:05:21.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,詛咒發動的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:21.28,0:05:24.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,她的樣子會更加扭扭捏捏 臉紅羞澀的啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:26.10,0:05:27.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我去叫澪大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:29.39,0:05:31.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,怎麼了？感覺有些不對..
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:33.03,0:05:34.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不好了 澪大人她！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:36.43,0:05:37.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那個笨蛋..
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:38.37,0:05:40.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,責任全在我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:40.33,0:05:42.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,如果至少能感知到她的所在位置的話..
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:42.79,0:05:45.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,而能感知澪大人的只有刃更先生而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:45.53,0:05:46.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我們走 萬理亞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:46.49,0:05:49.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不可以 刃更先生還沒完全恢復
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:49.75,0:05:50.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我自己去就..
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:52.87,0:05:53.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,萬理亞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:01.01,0:06:03.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,驅人魔法也施展完畢 這就行了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:05.00,0:06:07.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,萬理亞 刃更 對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:08.22,0:06:11.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,看來 你得出結論了呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:15.15,0:06:17.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,畢竟只要你一個人做出犧牲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:17.43,0:06:19.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,一切就會結束
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:19.31,0:06:21.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是啊 成為犧牲品的..
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:22.15,0:06:24.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,挺身戰鬥的只要我一人就足夠了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:30.92,0:06:32.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,還沒完！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:37.66,0:06:38.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,這樣就..
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:39.13,0:06:39.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,這樣就..
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:40.96,0:06:42.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,玩夠了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:44.98,0:06:46.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,相當美麗的火焰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:46.99,0:06:48.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,要我向部下下令試試麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:50.09,0:06:51.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你的那個火焰魔法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:52.01,0:06:53.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,和原勇者所沉睡的那個家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:54.20,0:06:56.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,試試看哪個能成為更美麗的火焰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:56.24,0:06:57.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你卑鄙！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:57.27,0:06:59.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,把他捲進來的是你啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:59.61,0:07:01.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,要怪的話就怪你自己吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:05.04,0:07:06.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你的目標是我吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:07.13,0:07:09.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,拜託你 不要向刃更他們出手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:10.45,0:07:13.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,很正確的判斷 交涉成立了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:14.80,0:07:15.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,伸出手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:17.76,0:07:18.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那麼走吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:19.15,0:07:20.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你打算把我帶去哪？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:20.30,0:07:21.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,去魔界
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:22.93,0:07:25.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我們的主人在等待你的到來..
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:28.10,0:07:28.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,野中？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:32.69,0:07:33.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,為什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:34.04,0:07:36.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,沒想到你會選擇幫她
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:37.10,0:07:37.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我..
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:46.61,0:07:50.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,只是絕不原諒傷害刃更的你而已！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:53.93,0:07:59.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,成瀨澪 你在屋頂上哭喊著對刃更一次次的道歉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:00.17,0:08:03.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,而現在你還打算犧牲自己
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:04.14,0:08:07.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我好像明白了為什麼刃更想要守護你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:09.05,0:08:10.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,憑你是無法打倒我的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:11.15,0:08:12.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你應該明白這一點吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:13.84,0:08:16.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那麼 這招如何！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:22.57,0:08:23.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你是如何打破障壁的？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:24.62,0:08:26.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,如果一擊無法斬斷的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:26.46,0:08:28.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,就斬到成功為止..僅此而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:30.53,0:08:34.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,難不成 在同一處精確疊加了數次斬擊？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:35.12,0:08:36.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,別小看勇者一族！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:41.51,0:08:44.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好啊 那就稍微陪你玩玩吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:44.65,0:08:45.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,危險！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:52.18,0:08:54.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,誒 能躲開那個啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:55.31,0:08:56.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那麼..
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:03.49,0:09:04.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,野中！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:06.18,0:09:07.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,還能..
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:08.55,0:09:11.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我還能戰鬥 因為這..
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:12.40,0:09:14.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,因為這條命是刃更救回來的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:16.14,0:09:19.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,為此我明明忍受了嚴酷的修行 已經變強了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:22.51,0:09:23.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,這就結束了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:25.13,0:09:26.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,住手 和野中無關
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:27.42,0:09:29.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你要我怎樣都行 所以..
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:29.64,0:09:30.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,這可不行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:31.08,0:09:34.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,妨礙任務進行的人就必須消失！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:36.70,0:09:39.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,討厭..不可以！！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:48.65,0:09:51.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,交給我吧 澪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:53.60,0:09:54.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,來吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:01.02,0:10:02.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,無次元的執行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:01.02,0:10:02.49,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\pos(640,640)}VanishingShift
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:02.64,0:10:04.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,能讓各種攻擊無效化..
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:04.91,0:10:10.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,這個力量甚至能讓存在以及事象本身消失於零次元
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:11.48,0:10:12.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,別害怕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:14.24,0:10:17.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,居然讓犧牲掉的遺骸都全部消失了..
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:18.28,0:10:18.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好危險
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:19.38,0:10:20.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,太可怕了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:20.36,0:10:21.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,太危險了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:21.66,0:10:23.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,為了不讓悲劇再度重演
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:24.27,0:10:27.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,應該把魔劍布倫希爾德和刃更幽禁起來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:28.03,0:10:29.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,放棄吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:32.59,0:10:33.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不要逃避
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:33.95,0:10:35.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,這是澪教會我的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:37.90,0:10:41.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,保護想保護的東西！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:53.40,0:10:55.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,刃更 那個力量..
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:55.86,0:10:58.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,雖然不完全 但這個程度的話沒有問題
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:59.74,0:11:01.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,看來我撐不了太久啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:11.10,0:11:11.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,原來如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:12.97,0:11:14.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我改變想法了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:15.03,0:11:17.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,最妨礙任務執行的存在..
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:18.08,0:11:20.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是你 東城刃更！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:28.71,0:11:29.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,就是現在！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:34.85,0:11:35.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,居然毫髮無傷？！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:36.20,0:11:37.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,得手了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:41.89,0:11:43.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,讓我的攻擊消失於無形的能力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:44.25,0:11:45.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那到底是什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:46.25,0:11:48.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,看來是僅僅用於反擊的能力呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:50.20,0:11:51.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,如果無限制地發動的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:52.25,0:11:54.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,應該擁有把這整個城鎮摧毀的潛能..
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:54.44,0:11:55.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,住口！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:55.70,0:11:58.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,但是這個情況下 反擊技是沒有意義的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:00.26,0:12:02.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,很遺憾 到此為止了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:03.33,0:12:06.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,嗯 是很遺憾 不過是你啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:06.77,0:12:07.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,萬理亞！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:13.24,0:12:14.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,夢魔麼！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:18.43,0:12:19.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,太遲了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:22.68,0:12:24.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,東城刃更！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:47.03,0:12:47.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,刃更
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:48.97,0:12:49.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,結束了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:53.45,0:12:55.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,澪大人！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:55.49,0:12:58.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我好擔心 好擔心您啊..
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:01.33,0:13:03.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,對不起 對不起哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:04.69,0:13:05.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,看來你沒事啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:06.36,0:13:06.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:07.28,0:13:08.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,謝謝..
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:09.27,0:13:09.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,怎麼了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:14.00,0:13:15.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,刃更！！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:22.92,0:13:27.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不..不要！！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:47.16,0:13:49.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,發生什麼事了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:51.80,0:13:52.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,澪！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:54.51,0:13:57.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,魔王威爾貝特的力量麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:57.92,0:13:59.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,刃更..
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:00.35,0:14:03.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,冷靜下來 你瞧 我沒事的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:03.65,0:14:05.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,全都結束了 所以..
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:05.71,0:14:06.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不行啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:06.75,0:14:07.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:07.63,0:14:10.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不行啊 光是抑制住力量就很勉強了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:11.07,0:14:12.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,完全停不下來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:12.90,0:14:16.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,重力波麼..要是繼續失控下去的話..
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:16.84,0:14:17.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,拜託你 刃更
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:18.11,0:14:20.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我沒法繼續壓制失控的力量了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:21.27,0:14:21.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,所以..
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:22.24,0:14:23.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,等等 別放棄！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:24.13,0:14:29.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,沒時間了 在我把世界破壞之前..拜託你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:30.51,0:14:31.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,殺了我吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:35.57,0:14:36.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我拒絕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:38.02,0:14:38.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,笨..笨蛋！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:39.05,0:14:41.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,該保護哪一邊根本不用考慮吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:41.72,0:14:43.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我已經不是勇者了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:43.47,0:14:46.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,但是我卻是你的家人 是你的哥哥！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:47.50,0:14:48.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,而做哥哥的啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:49.45,0:14:53.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,即便與世界為敵 也至少必須保護好自己的妹妹啊！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:55.46,0:14:56.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我會帶你回去的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:57.03,0:14:57.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,誒？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:58.02,0:14:59.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,絕對會帶你回去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:00.80,0:15:02.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你要和我一起回去那個家！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:03.83,0:15:07.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,做妹妹的 在這種時候就閉上嘴讓哥哥保護吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:12.52,0:15:16.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,拜託你 救救我 哥哥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:19.43,0:15:23.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,完全的無次元的執行 應該能夠拯救澪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:25.67,0:15:28.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,看穿澪那股失控力量的根源
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:28.73,0:15:30.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,只消除那個根源
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:34.05,0:15:36.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,等著我 我馬上讓它消失
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:37.05,0:15:39.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,直到你的所有痛苦和悲傷..
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:40.06,0:15:41.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,歸零為止！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:47.27,0:15:49.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,無次元的執行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:59.85,0:16:00.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,回家吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:01.59,0:16:02.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:11.99,0:16:12.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:14.07,0:16:15.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,啊 你好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:16.62,0:16:19.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,前陣子..那個..刃更呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:20.15,0:16:21.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,他還睡著呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:21.67,0:16:24.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,畢竟傷都沒好就那麼逞強..
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:27.01,0:16:27.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,這是？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:27.81,0:16:29.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,村裏流傳的秘藥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:29.79,0:16:32.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,對於繼承了勇者之血的刃更應該更有效果
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:33.37,0:16:34.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不好意思還讓你特地送來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:35.15,0:16:36.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,請進請進
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:37.12,0:16:39.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我只是要把這個拿來而已 請保重
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:47.63,0:16:48.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,無次元的執行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:52.51,0:16:56.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那個..和那時一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:58.50,0:17:01.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不對..他控制住了力量
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:05.36,0:17:08.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你終於..終於能夠面對了呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:12.44,0:17:15.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,歡迎回來 刃更
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:18.54,0:17:20.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,學校也是一周沒來了呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:20.44,0:17:22.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,明明沒必要連澪都請這麼久的假啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:23.13,0:17:24.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,有什麼關係嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:24.85,0:17:27.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,因為對外宣稱是我們一起得了風熱感冒啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:27.26,0:17:28.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,就是說啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:28.63,0:17:30.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,要不是野中柚希小姐拿來的回復藥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:31.06,0:17:34.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,以及澪大人細心又貼心的照顧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:34.98,0:17:36.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你怎能免於住院之苦呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:37.27,0:17:38.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,萬理亞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:43.48,0:17:46.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,把這篇文章從頭分解 第一句的主語..
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:53.34,0:17:54.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,喲 小刃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:54.75,0:17:56.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,大病初癒的傢伙可以翹課嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:56.98,0:18:00.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,能打開這裏門鎖的不只你一人啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:01.00,0:18:04.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,哎 學校這麼大 肯定是有別人啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:04.93,0:18:06.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你沒事吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:07.51,0:18:09.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,嗯？你說那天晚上的事嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:10.06,0:18:11.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那回你搞什麼啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:11.09,0:18:13.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不但突然朝著我的心窩來了一肘子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:13.54,0:18:15.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,還把人丟在那不管
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:15.53,0:18:16.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不是指這件事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:17.81,0:18:21.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,在公園 我似乎砍了你不少刀呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:23.67,0:18:24.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你指什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:25.28,0:18:28.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,如果打算抵死不認的話 你可別後悔哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:34.09,0:18:35.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,什麼時候發覺的？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:36.10,0:18:39.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那晚在學校裏 你說了澪暈倒的事吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:40.38,0:18:42.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,她突然倒下真是讓人嚇一跳呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:43.01,0:18:45.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,而且臉通通紅的 好像很難為情的樣子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:46.90,0:18:49.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,正常來說 臉色通紅身形不穩的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:49.78,0:18:51.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,應該會聯想到感冒才對吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:52.30,0:18:54.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,哎呀 看到成瀨奇怪的反應
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:55.44,0:18:58.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,馬上就想到這事和她那隨從夢魔有關呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:58.73,0:19:02.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,由於忍住不笑太辛苦了 結果不小心說漏嘴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:03.61,0:19:05.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,哎 搞砸了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:07.14,0:19:09.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那你要怎麼辦啊 小刃？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:16.85,0:19:17.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我選擇不動手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:18.62,0:19:21.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,現在的我不一定贏得了你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:21.47,0:19:23.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,而我倒是想跟你交涉一下呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:24.68,0:19:25.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,交涉？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:25.69,0:19:29.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,嗯 你是現任魔王派派來監視澪的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:30.67,0:19:34.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,而你平時暗中監視 一有機會就促發澪的覺醒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:35.15,0:19:36.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那就是你的任務
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:36.85,0:19:39.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,在公園差點就成功了說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:39.96,0:19:41.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,但是你失敗了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:43.29,0:19:44.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,一旦得知你的失敗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:45.31,0:19:47.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,現任魔王派一定會派來更強的傢伙吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:48.61,0:19:50.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我還不想和那種傢伙打交道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:50.75,0:19:55.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,原來如此 叫我繼續擔任監視者 權當沒事發生麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:55.79,0:19:57.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,畢竟憑你和那個夢魔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:57.15,0:20:00.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,完全可以向現任魔王派透露我失手的消息呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:01.06,0:20:02.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,這筆交易不賴吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:02.84,0:20:06.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我們可是敵人 什麼時候會背叛都不奇怪哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:07.18,0:20:08.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我相信你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:09.17,0:20:10.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你這麼說有什麼根據？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:11.34,0:20:13.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,就因為我現在還活得好好的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:15.46,0:20:17.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,襲擊我的刺客沒有殺我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:18.62,0:20:20.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,短劍明顯避開了我的要害
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:21.45,0:20:23.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那只是你命大而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:23.53,0:20:24.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,還有萬理亞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:25.30,0:20:26.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,之前她獨自狩獵魔物之時
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:26.93,0:20:29.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你們應該有很多機會除掉她才對
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:30.78,0:20:32.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,這就是我相信你的理由
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:37.80,0:20:39.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你的想像力還真豐富
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:40.59,0:20:41.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,但是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:41.68,0:20:45.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,由於這次的事件 我的處境也越發險惡起來了呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:45.43,0:20:47.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,目前我就同意了吧 小刃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:47.94,0:20:49.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,同意你這個主意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:49.48,0:20:50.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,幫大忙了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:53.51,0:20:55.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那麼我差不多該回去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:57.38,0:21:00.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我說 瀧川 殺死澪養父母的傢伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:00.78,0:21:01.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你知道是誰麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:03.82,0:21:07.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,等等啊 單方面提供情報可不公平哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:11.62,0:21:12.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是佐基爾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:13.76,0:21:14.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,佐基爾？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:15.30,0:21:18.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,他是成瀨的前任監視者
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:18.68,0:21:20.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不過他是個不甘寂寞的傢伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:21.41,0:21:23.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那傢伙一定會採取行動的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:26.86,0:21:27.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,澪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:28.34,0:21:29.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,再見
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:29.46,0:21:30.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,服了你們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:30.90,0:21:33.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,兩人一起在這種地方逃課
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:34.02,0:21:36.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,天氣很好 自然就…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:37.14,0:21:38.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,和瀧川說了些什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:38.90,0:21:41.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,沒什麼 天氣真好那些啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:43.36,0:21:47.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我 得救後的謝禮 還未給刃更
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:48.08,0:21:49.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,現在提起來做什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:50.28,0:21:52.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,就是 就是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:58.74,0:21:59.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:00.14,0:22:00.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,柚希
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:01.66,0:22:03.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,野中 為什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:04.24,0:22:07.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,一有空就向刃更拋媚眼啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:07.38,0:22:09.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,誰沒事拋媚眼啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:09.44,0:22:11.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,刃更 請吃這個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:11.48,0:22:15.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,便當啊 說起來 你從小以來就擅長料理啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:15.64,0:22:16.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,等等
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:17.22,0:22:20.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我也打算等會和刃更一起吃午餐啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:20.92,0:22:21.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,油膩火鍋？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:22.24,0:22:24.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,久等了 澪大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:24.62,0:22:25.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,萬里亞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:25.72,0:22:27.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,便當的準備完成了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:27.76,0:22:28.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,來吧 澪大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:28.76,0:22:32.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不能輸給這種無表情系的青梅竹馬女人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:32.36,0:22:35.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,給刃更哥做那樣 餵食
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:35.90,0:22:39.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,開玩笑吧 為什麼我要給那種人…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:42.64,0:22:43.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,又來了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:43.78,0:22:47.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,沒辦法了 唯有刃更歌給澪大人餵食了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:47.76,0:22:50.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,對澪大人說 「啊」
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:51.00,0:22:52.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,來吧 刃更哥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:52.44,0:22:56.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,用這個極粗的香腸稍微粗暴地向澪大人可愛的嘴唇塞去…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:56.88,0:22:58.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,誰能做啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:58.60,0:22:59.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,都這樣了還說什麼啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:00.06,0:23:04.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,刃更哥 澪大人和我都一起做過更厲害的事的夥伴啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:04.66,0:23:08.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,前段時間 在浴室裸體蛋糕PLAY
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:08.04,0:23:10.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,討厭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:10.34,0:23:11.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,怎麼回事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:11.90,0:23:13.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不知道嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:13.52,0:23:16.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,刃更哥前段時間成為澪大人的主人了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:17.36,0:23:20.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那種事不行啊 絕對不能饒恕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:20.82,0:23:24.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,澪大人的身心都成為刃更哥的僕人了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:24.12,0:23:25.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,在我的眼前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:26.02,0:23:28.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,等下 萬里亞你擅自說什麼啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:28.74,0:23:29.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,殺你一百回哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:30.08,0:23:33.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你們收斂下啊 刃更是我的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:34.06,0:23:36.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,哈！ 什麼時候變成你的啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:36.64,0:23:38.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:39.62,0:23:40.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你們啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:43.44,0:23:45.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,嗯 收到他發來的郵件了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:47.51,0:23:48.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,所以我說了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:49.11,0:23:52.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,只要有個契機 那傢伙就一定會重新站起來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:53.42,0:23:54.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,畢竟刃更是我和..
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:55.57,0:23:57.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,她們的兒子啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:58.91,0:24:00.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,嗯 對了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:01.82,0:24:06.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我不在的這段期間 幫我照看刃更和澪他們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:10.58,0:24:12.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,別因為這點程度就滿足哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:12.92,0:24:15.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,刃更 不光是澪..
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:15.85,0:24:20.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,誰都不能從過去和命運中逃脫啊..
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:17.50,0:02:17.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:52.50,0:25:57.36,title,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\an8}下回 早晨的妹之魔王無雙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:17.50,0:02:17.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:17.50,0:02:17.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:17.50,0:02:17.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:17.50,0:02:17.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:17.50,0:02:17.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:17.50,0:02:17.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:17.50,0:02:17.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:22.82,0:24:24.37,ED_jp,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,もう一度会いたい
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:24.37,0:24:25.71,ED_jp,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,なんて想いは
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:25.71,0:24:29.69,ED_jp,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,全部閉じ込めてしまおう
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:30.03,0:24:36.51,ED_jp,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,この胸の 奥にずっと
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:48.35,0:24:50.72,ED_jp,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,夢の中では
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:50.98,0:24:55.44,ED_jp,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,素直に言えた言葉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:55.90,0:24:58.78,ED_jp,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,何度も練習
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:59.34,0:25:01.69,ED_jp,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,気づけばいつも
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:01.96,0:25:06.45,ED_jp,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,傍で笑ってるキミが
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:06.82,0:25:09.65,ED_jp,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,あたりまえになってた
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:09.93,0:25:14.80,ED_jp,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,ああ　瞳閉じても消えない
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:15.04,0:25:19.80,ED_jp,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,影に　何度も言うから
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:20.35,0:25:21.95,ED_jp,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,もう一度会いたい
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:21.95,0:25:23.19,ED_jp,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,大切な人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:23.48,0:25:25.98,ED_jp,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,共に生きていきたい
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:26.13,0:25:28.67,ED_jp,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,たとえ世界から
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:28.90,0:25:31.24,ED_jp,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,刃を向けられても
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:31.24,0:25:32.84,ED_jp,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,もう二度とこの手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:33.01,0:25:34.26,ED_jp,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,離さないと
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:34.26,0:25:38.25,ED_jp,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,夢の外で言えた言葉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:38.69,0:25:45.32,ED_jp,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,いつまでも　笑顔のまま
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:17.50,0:02:17.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,
